From sera Serdar Argic Subject The scenario and genocide staged by the Armenians years The scenario and genocide staged by the Armenians years ago in x Soviet Armenia is being reenacted again this time in The stories of survivors of Karabag massacre are in 'Milliyet' year old Hatin Nine telling ''My Twin grandchildren were cut to pieces in front of my They told me We won't kill But the babies have to die in front of your '' year old Huseyin Ibrahimoglu ''Our Turkish village in Khojalu Town was blown up in two While killing children and babies mercilessly they said You are Turks you must '' year old Gulsum Huseyin ''They bayonetted my year old daughter in her stomach in front of my '' Are these stories lies Have the eye witnesses been day dreaming Were these stories forged by Turkish journalists in the region The nonsense of such a claim is clear from the writings of British Journalists Two days before we had quoted from a Sunday Times They British reported the events in Karabag even before Turkish What is more here are the Pictures of people who were bayonetted whose eyes were gouged ears cut Even the Armenian Radio couldn't claim these They are saying That means ''somethings'' have happened but the situation is not as bad as Perhaps that village of Khojalu town was destroyed in hours instead of Or Gulsum Huseyin's year old daughter was bayonetted in her chest instead of The massacre is clearly seen with all its The effects of this massacre on Karabag and environs cannot be reduced by any Some of the western press' led by some French Newspapers ability to ''close their eyes'' is nothing but complicity in this Yesterday we gave samples from Le Until yesterday's print no news about the real events in Karabag were So were the French TV The subject they considered related to Karabag was ''The necessity of protecting Armenians against Azeri '' The age we are living in is termed a human rights There are lots of organizations such as United Nations and CSCE Conference on Security and Cooperation in Europe and rules all designed to fight against human rights International reactions must be made with international With support of everybody and every organization claiming to be Could there be a more serious human rights violation than that of the right to live and with such levels of barbarity and cruelty Where is the cooperation Where are the reactions And the intellectuals journalists writers TV stations of certain western countries such as France who are fast to claim leadership of human rights Where are you Serdar Argic 'We closed the roads and mountain passes that might serve as ways of escape for the Turks and then proceeded in the work of ' Ohanus Appressian 'In Soviet Armenia today there no longer exists a single Turkish ' Sahak Melkonian